1
00:00:24,190 --> 00:00:25,600
Your Highness, we've arrived.

2
00:00:32,980 --> 00:00:37,220
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

3
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,912
- Welcome home,
- Welcome home,

4
00:00:44,944 --> 00:00:47,504
- Commandery Princess Zhaoning.
- Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

5
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,240
I...

6
00:00:51,710 --> 00:00:53,390
greet Your Highness.

7
00:00:55,110 --> 00:00:56,150
Please rise, Uncle Qing.

8
00:00:57,110 --> 00:00:58,030
Your Highness.

9
00:00:58,032 --> 00:00:59,570
It's been many years since we last met,

10
00:00:59,584 --> 00:01:01,490
and you're still
as healthy and strong as ever.

11
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,710
I've always been worried about

12
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:05,590
the Duke, the Heir, and Your Highness

13
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:07,480
so far away in the northwest.

14
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:09,640
Greetings, Xihe.

15
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:15,700
(Shen Yingruo,
the Duke of Wei's second daughter)

16
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:17,840
Rise.

17
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,790
This way, Your Highness.

18
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:31,060
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

19
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:57,824
=Blossoms of Power=

20
00:02:57,830 --> 00:03:00,580
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

21
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:03,620
=Episode 3=

22
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:06,150
Jing was careless.

23
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,190
Someone exposed him.

24
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:10,432
(Xiao, the Duke of Wei's Concubine)
Shen Xihe is bound to suspect me.

25
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,150
What should I do?

26
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,840
She didn't die.

27
00:03:13,888 --> 00:03:15,600
What can she possibly do to you?

28
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:17,470
Don't panic.

29
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:19,300
(Fragrant Snow and Auspicious Clouds)

30
00:03:45,168 --> 00:03:47,040
Your Highness,
you've had a long journey.

31
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,710
Why not return to your room and rest?

32
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:49,360
Mo Yu,

33
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:51,360
throw Xiao out.

34
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:52,680
How dare you!

35
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:54,400
Madam!

36
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,000
How dare you lay a hand on me!

37
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,016
Believe it or not,
I'll have your hand cut off!

38
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,630
Shen Xihe,

39
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,960
have you lost your mind?

40
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,240
How dare you treat me like this!

41
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:05,000
The eastern courtyard

42
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,960
is reserved for the lady of the house.

43
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:09,030
If you knew your place,

44
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:11,310
you wouldn't
be humiliating yourself today.

45
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,080
Uncle Qing,

46
00:04:14,710 --> 00:04:16,160
throw these servants

47
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:17,270
and maids out as well.

48
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:18,390
Yes.

49
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,560
Men!

50
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,510
Throw them all out.

51
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,160
Let go of me!

52
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,040
Let go!

53
00:04:24,050 --> 00:04:25,190
Please calm your anger, Xihe.

54
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,480
Please leave Mother some...

55
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,390
Who is your mother?

56
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,310
Please spare the Concubine's dignity.

57
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,760
I'll persuade
the Concubine to move out today.

58
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,830
Don't beg her.

59
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,370
Shen Xihe, you have
no respect for your elders

60
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:46,360
and no regard for rank!

61
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:48,630
My elders?

62
00:04:49,008 --> 00:04:51,690
I am Commandery Princess Zhaoning,
personally invested by His Majesty.

63
00:04:51,824 --> 00:04:53,750
You are nothing more
than my father's concubine.

64
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:55,720
You didn't even bow before me,
yet I let it pass.

65
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,430
And you dare lecture me about rank?

66
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,270
I am Prince Kang's sister.

67
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:01,488
The Marquis of Xuanping
is my maternal grandfather.

68
00:05:01,872 --> 00:05:04,336
Yingruo was also invested
as a County Princess by His Majesty.

69
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,304
What gives you the right
to look down on us?

70
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,570
Back then, my father was summoned

71
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,270
to the imperial capital
to be rewarded by His Majesty.

72
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,480
You bribed a palace attendant

73
00:05:10,870 --> 00:05:13,000
to drug the liquor
bestowed by His Majesty

74
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,160
and got into his bed.

75
00:05:15,232 --> 00:05:17,104
My father refused
to take you as his concubine,

76
00:05:17,104 --> 00:05:19,536
so you had Prince Kang's Manor
secretly spread the rumor

77
00:05:19,552 --> 00:05:21,430
that he would
take you as his equal wife.

78
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,640
The news reached the northwest.

79
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,040
My mother was so distressed

80
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,360
that she went
into labor at eight months.

81
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,390
She died after giving birth to me.

82
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,750
My father was devastated.

83
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,430
He swore never to remarry.

84
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,920
If you hadn't been carrying his child,

85
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,432
you wouldn't even have been worthy
of becoming his concubine.

86
00:05:38,512 --> 00:05:39,720
You...

87
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,310
Xihe,

88
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,870
please calm your anger.

89
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,510
Why are you kneeling to her?

90
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:50,750
Shen Xihe,

91
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,000
you humiliated me today.

92
00:05:54,288 --> 00:05:57,184
Do you think you'll have an easy life
in the imperial capital from now on?

93
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,160
You've made an enemy of me today.

94
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,390
Prince Kang's Manor
will make you repay this a thousandfold!

95
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:07,190
An enemy?

96
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,750
Not just today.

97
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:11,830
Ling Long, the maid,

98
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:13,000
works for you.

99
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:17,920
Ling... Ling Long?

100
00:06:18,096 --> 00:06:19,920
I... I don't know
who you're talking about.

101
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,160
She was the vile servant
who pushed me into the river

102
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:24,950
under orders from you
and Prince Kang's Manor.

103
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,750
How dare you falsely accuse me!

104
00:06:29,510 --> 00:06:30,680
If I had died,

105
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:33,600
your daughter would've become
the Duke of Wei's only daughter.

106
00:06:33,984 --> 00:06:36,240
Then you could've risen in status
through your daughter.

107
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,630
It was your only chance
to shed your status

108
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:39,480
as a concubine.

109
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,480
You and Prince Kang's Manor

110
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:44,070
have always
been plotting to get rid of me.

111
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:47,750
But

112
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,360
you're not worthy

113
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,870
of being my enemy.

114
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,920
You wretch!

115
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,270
Wretch!

116
00:06:55,408 --> 00:06:57,600
You looked so innocent and fragile
when you were little.

117
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,070
It was all an act!

118
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,240
You're incredibly scheming.

119
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:03,040
You're even more venomous than a viper.

120
00:07:03,072 --> 00:07:04,830
As long as Prince Kang's Manor
still stands,

121
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,500
I'll make sure
you die a miserable death.

122
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:07,720
Enough!

123
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,870
Take her away.

124
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:09,920
Drive her out!

125
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,040
Throw her out.

126
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,384
- Take them all away.
- Move!

127
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,190
Xihe,

128
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,480
please spare the Concubine this once.

129
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,870
Did you know

130
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,560
about Ling Long?

131
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,510
What do you mean?

132
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:32,070
It seems you really knew nothing.

133
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,830
Think carefully.

134
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:35,680
Are you a Shen,

135
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,190
or a Xiao?

136
00:07:46,912 --> 00:07:48,784
Your Highness,
by dealing with Xiao like this,

137
00:07:48,816 --> 00:07:50,270
I'm afraid you'll only make enemies.

138
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:52,304
Have you ever seen
wolves keep company with dogs,

139
00:07:52,336 --> 00:07:53,408
or tigers walk with foxes?

140
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,680
They're beneath me.

141
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,248
There's no point wasting time on them.

142
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:04,830
Let's go.

143
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:05,240
Go.

144
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:10,100
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

145
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:11,720
She was really thrown out.

146
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,680
Have you heard?

147
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,830
All these years,

148
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,270
everyone thought
she was the Duke's wife.

149
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,190
Turns out she was only a concubine.

150
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,040
Goodness.

151
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,310
She was really thrown out.

152
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,560
How humiliating.

153
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,830
How can anyone be so bold?

154
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,510
Xiao is still a favored concubine.

155
00:08:29,936 --> 00:08:32,120
How could they throw her
out of the manor like this?

156
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:35,424
I rather admire

157
00:08:35,430 --> 00:08:37,790
Commandery Princess Zhaoning's spirit
of settling every score

158
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:39,520
and refusing to be taken advantage of.

159
00:08:41,910 --> 00:08:43,440
Compared with those meek

160
00:08:43,488 --> 00:08:44,896
and long-suffering young ladies,

161
00:08:44,976 --> 00:08:46,224
the commandery princess

162
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,510
is rare for her strength and courage.

163
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,910
This is clearly ruthless

164
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,910
and merciless.

165
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:54,480
How did it become strength
and courage to you?

166
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,320
Speaking of which,

167
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,480
the commandery princess
will soon meet the princes.

168
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,840
Who do you think

169
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:02,510
she'll give the Rouge Ledger to?

170
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,720
She will surely give it to me.

171
00:09:11,540 --> 00:09:14,820
(Chenning Hall)

172
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,080
Your Majesty.

173
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,120
(Xiao Juechong, Emperor Youning)
By all rights,

174
00:09:20,256 --> 00:09:23,152
the Crown Prince should come
to the palace to pay his respects.

175
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:26,720
Yet Your Majesty is personally
visiting the Eastern Palace.

176
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,510
Huayong has been frail since childhood.

177
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:33,120
This journey back to the palace
must have been exhausting.

178
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:33,960
I...

179
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:37,750
truly don't want him to be too tired.

180
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,790
I'll go prepare at once

181
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:42,190
for the visit to the Eastern Palace.

182
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,150
His Majesty has arrived.

183
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,480
Father.

184
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,000
My Huayong has returned.

185
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,030
I already

186
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,790
exempted you
from these formalities, didn't I?

187
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:12,320
Come.

188
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,910
Huayong,

189
00:10:22,224 --> 00:10:23,670
now that you're back in the palace,

190
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:24,550
if anything happens,

191
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,550
send someone to inform me at once.

192
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,000
Father,

193
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,910
ever since Mother passed away,

194
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,150
you issued a decree

195
00:10:33,184 --> 00:10:35,152
never to appoint
another Empress in this lifetime.

196
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,720
I understand

197
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,320
that you did it so

198
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,928
no one could shake my position
as Crown Prince of the Eastern Palace.

199
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,720
You also made all the princes' names

200
00:10:43,376 --> 00:10:44,870
avoid "Hua" and change to "Chang,"

201
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:46,630
so they would not conflict with mine.

202
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:49,480
My daily provisions are also

203
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,720
arranged to match Father's.

204
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,240
But I

205
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,080
sometimes truly do not understand.

206
00:10:55,616 --> 00:10:57,000
Why would someone as frail as I am

207
00:10:57,440 --> 00:11:00,000
receive such generous care
and protection from Father?

208
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,270
Huayong.

209
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,870
I...

210
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:06,670
still remember

211
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,910
you with your hair in two buns.

212
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:13,080
So innocent and carefree.

213
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:18,360
You were exceptionally gifted
from a young age.

214
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:21,390
Whatever you learned,

215
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,910
you never forgot it

216
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,270
and mastered it with ease.

217
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:28,150
You were hailed
as an unparalleled prodigy.

218
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:30,670
You are my

219
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,670
most beloved son.

220
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,510
Huayong,

221
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:39,120
don't overthink it.

222
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,150
Just...

223
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:43,720
focus on recovering.

224
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:44,960
Only then

225
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:48,750
can I entrust the realm

226
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,120
to you.

227
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,790
Thank you, Father.

228
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:02,940
(Auspicious Radiance)

229
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,120
Tian Yuan,

230
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:14,240
what really happened back then?

231
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:15,270
Your Highness,

232
00:12:15,584 --> 00:12:17,320
when the case
was thoroughly investigated,

233
00:12:17,504 --> 00:12:19,984
after Steward Zhao
of the Palace Food Bureau confessed,

234
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,390
she suddenly died in prison.

235
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,510
The case became unsolved,

236
00:12:23,792 --> 00:12:25,030
with no evidence left behind.

237
00:12:30,030 --> 00:12:32,670
This poison was made from
more than a dozen exotic toxins.

238
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,600
It wouldn't kill at once,

239
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:38,670
but would make its victim suffer

240
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,000
excruciating pain day after day.

241
00:12:42,270 --> 00:12:43,750
I must find out

242
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,630
who this person really is,

243
00:12:46,390 --> 00:12:48,150
and why they poisoned me.

244
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,270
So close to Father,

245
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:52,670
yet hidden within the court.

246
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,840
It must be someone of great power

247
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,480
to have stayed hidden for so long.

248
00:12:57,500 --> 00:12:58,790
If I don't uncover this person,

249
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:00,510
they'll remain a grave threat

250
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:02,750
to Father and the realm.

251
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:04,910
They must be eliminated.

252
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,630
Greetings, Your Majesty.

253
00:13:23,696 --> 00:13:25,088
Greetings, Grand Empress Dowager.

254
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,500
May Your Majesty
be blessed with good health.

255
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,740
May Grand Empress Dowager
be blessed with good health.

256
00:13:27,750 --> 00:13:29,824
No need for formalities,
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

257
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:30,720
Rise.

258
00:13:30,768 --> 00:13:33,488
(Grand Empress Dowager Meng)
Thank you, Your Majesty, and Grand Empress Dowager.

259
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:36,910
Your father has sent you
to the imperial capital.

260
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:40,240
I will take good care of you.

261
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,670
From today onward,

262
00:13:41,728 --> 00:13:43,340
your food, clothing,
and daily provisions

263
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:45,024
shall follow the rank of a princess.

264
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,312
Thank you, Your Majesty.

265
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:53,740
(Consort Liang)

266
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:55,820
(Noble Consort Rong)

267
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,120
Prince Yu has arrived.

268
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:44,630
I wish Father and Grandmother

269
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:45,750
good health and a long life.

270
00:14:46,048 --> 00:14:47,472
May you enjoy eight thousand springs,

271
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,870
and eight thousand autumns.

272
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:51,030
Changyu,

273
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:53,390
you're always late.

274
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,510
Take a seat.

275
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,220
Your Highness has traveled
all the way from the northwest.

276
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,150
You must be exhausted.

277
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:12,480
Allow me to offer you a toast.

278
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,960
Thank you, Prince Yu.

279
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:22,960
Your Highness,

280
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:24,870
the imperial capital

281
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,510
has many delightful places.

282
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,480
If Your Highness has the time,

283
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:30,320
allow me to be your guide.

284
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:32,270
May I show Your Highness
around the capital?

285
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:34,550
I wouldn't dare trouble Prince Yu.

286
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,910
It would be

287
00:15:36,630 --> 00:15:38,000
my honor.

288
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,790
Your Majesty, look.

289
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:43,120
Changyu and the commandery princess
seem to have hit it off.

290
00:15:43,136 --> 00:15:45,136
They just met,
and they're already getting along.

291
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:48,360
I've long heard Commandery Princess
Zhaoning is a peerless beauty.

292
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:49,840
Now that I've seen her,

293
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,600
I can't take my eyes off her.

294
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:53,750
She's a delight to behold.

295
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:56,960
Your Majesty,

296
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:58,910
just look.

297
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,750
They're all speaking
with hidden motives.

298
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:02,480
They all want Zhaoning

299
00:16:02,630 --> 00:16:04,670
as their daughter-in-law.

300
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,150
I have a request.

301
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:16,380
I ask Your Majesty to grant it.

302
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,600
Speak freely.

303
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:19,320
The husband I marry

304
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,550
must be the one I love.

305
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:27,200
So you intend
to choose your own husband?

306
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,600
I wish to marry a man

307
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,120
who knows and cherishes me,

308
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:32,750
so we may share a happy marriage.

309
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:34,670
If husband and wife are at odds,

310
00:16:34,750 --> 00:16:37,030
the household will know no peace.

311
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:40,200
At worst, it will drive a wedge
between the two families.

312
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,000
The Shen family has been honored

313
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,690
with a marriage
into the imperial family.

314
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,808
Such a matter
must be considered with great care.

315
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,510
My only wish is to marry for love.

316
00:16:47,856 --> 00:16:49,872
I ask Your Majesty to grant my request.

317
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,030
Zhaoning,

318
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,150
let me ask you this.

319
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:56,000
What if the man you love

320
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,550
doesn't love you back?

321
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,080
What would you do?

322
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:01,240
I would respect the prince's wishes.

323
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,360
Zhaoning,

324
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:04,200
after saying that,

325
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:07,720
aren't you afraid you'll become
the laughingstock of the entire palace?

326
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:08,920
Grand Empress Dowager,

327
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,960
to care about what others say and think

328
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,110
is to imprison myself.

329
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:14,310
That's not who I am.

330
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,790
I seek mutual love.

331
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,480
The princes should have the same wish.

332
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:20,200
I'm certain

333
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,750
I'll find the right man.

334
00:17:22,830 --> 00:17:23,510
Father,

335
00:17:24,848 --> 00:17:26,270
the commandery princess has vision,

336
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,030
courage,

337
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,030
and magnanimity.

338
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:30,510
She truly proves women
are no less than men.

339
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:33,030
I'd like to ask Father to grant

340
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,890
the commandery princess's request.

341
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,720
I grant it.

342
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:44,550
Once you've chosen

343
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:47,510
the right husband
from among the princes,

344
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:51,510
I will arrange the marriage.

345
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:53,030
The whole realm will know of it.

346
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,030
Thank you, Your Majesty.

347
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:12,680
Your remarks

348
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:14,110
in the hall just now

349
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,510
truly impressed me.

350
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:17,790
You flatter me, Your Highness.

351
00:18:17,888 --> 00:18:19,590
Since you wish
to choose your own husband,

352
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:22,030
how much do you know about my brothers?

353
00:18:22,976 --> 00:18:24,880
I've only just arrived
in the imperial capital.

354
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,510
I don't know much about them.

355
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:30,070
In that case,

356
00:18:30,790 --> 00:18:32,720
let me tell you a little about them.

357
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:33,504
What do you say?

358
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,590
I'd be glad to hear.

359
00:18:37,232 --> 00:18:39,350
There are currently
five princes of marriageable age.

360
00:18:39,376 --> 00:18:40,920
My second brother is Xiao Changmin.

361
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,720
His wife, Lady Yu,

362
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:43,960
passed away a few years ago.

363
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:45,640
He has never remarried.

364
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,000
The Yu family
still treats him like a son-in-law.

365
00:18:48,070 --> 00:18:49,510
The two families remain close.

366
00:18:49,568 --> 00:18:51,110
My fifth brother is Xiao Changqing,

367
00:18:51,110 --> 00:18:52,630
and my ninth brother is Xiao Changying.

368
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:54,400
Their mother is Noble Consort Rong.

369
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:56,270
Their uncle,
the Duke of Ying, guards Anlan.

370
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:58,016
He commands a hundred thousand cavalry.

371
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,376
My sixth brother is Xiao Changyu,

372
00:18:59,408 --> 00:19:00,544
a man of immortal grace.

373
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:03,500
His mother, Consort Liang,
is unmatched in the inner palace.

374
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,270
Ye Qi, Commander-in-Chief of Hexi,

375
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,790
is Consort Liang's cousin.

376
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:10,030
(These princes are backed
either by powerful families)

377
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:11,400
(or wield military power.)

378
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,960
(That means
too many people rely on them.)

379
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:16,590
(Entrusting the Rouge Ledger
to any of them)

380
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:17,880
(wouldn't be prudent.)

381
00:19:23,424 --> 00:19:24,790
Your Highness is truly fortunate.

382
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,960
Whoever you marry

383
00:19:28,048 --> 00:19:29,270
will make a wonderful match.

384
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:33,030
Why don't you
introduce yourself, Your Highness?

385
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:37,440
I'm different.

386
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,480
I've been away from court for years.

387
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,550
All alone.

388
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,350
Just a frail,

389
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,680
overlooked,

390
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,200
idle Crown Prince.

391
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,960
Your Highness holds
the position of Crown Prince.

392
00:19:49,072 --> 00:19:50,550
You enjoy His Majesty's favor.

393
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:51,960
You're far too modest.

394
00:19:54,768 --> 00:19:56,160
Thank you for your kind words.

395
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:59,960
Do you still remember our agreement?

396
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:02,260
Let's meet at
the Eastern Palace another day.

397
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:04,550
I'll be there.

398
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:22,110
Why didn't Prince Lie
send a calling card?

399
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:22,680
Answer me.

400
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,000
Where is the Rouge Ledger now?

401
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:26,750
Prince Lie needn't ask.

402
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,720
I'll give it to the right person.

403
00:20:29,110 --> 00:20:29,750
Who is it?

404
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:32,070
Which prince has won your favor?

405
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:33,200
That's none of your concern.

406
00:20:34,510 --> 00:20:35,720
May I ask, Prince Lie,

407
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:36,830
if the Rouge Ledger

408
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:38,720
contains members
of Noble Consort Rong's family,

409
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,680
could you truly
set personal feelings aside

410
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,880
and uphold justice?

411
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,030
Just answer me.

412
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,920
Which prince has won your favor?

413
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,030
Is it Changyu?

414
00:20:46,784 --> 00:20:47,590
See the guest out.

415
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:48,510
Wait.

416
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:56,750
This was your favorite

417
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,920
when you came to the imperial capital

418
00:20:59,110 --> 00:21:00,480
with your father as a child.

419
00:21:01,070 --> 00:21:01,720
Give it a try.

420
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,980
(Tao Zhuanxian, Shen Xihe's
Maternal Grandfather, Censor)

421
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:06,260
(Tao Yuan, Shen Xihe's Uncle)

422
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:07,580
(Madam Zhang, Shen Xihe's Aunt)

423
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:11,720
Isn't it good?

424
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:18,110
You drove Xiao out of the manor?

425
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:21,510
She's now

426
00:21:21,720 --> 00:21:24,160
back at Prince Kang's Manor.

427
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:27,070
If she gives you any more trouble,

428
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:29,110
you must tell me.

429
00:21:30,830 --> 00:21:32,880
Aren't you afraid
of offending Prince Kang's Manor?

430
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,880
Afraid?

431
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,750
Afraid of what?

432
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:38,920
Ever since Xiao
caused my daughter to die,

433
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,720
I'm afraid of nothing.

434
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,960
All these years,

435
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,830
I've stood against Prince Kang.

436
00:21:44,830 --> 00:21:46,880
I've never forgotten to seek justice

437
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,830
for my daughter.

438
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:50,070
They may have forgotten

439
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,110
my sister's life,

440
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:53,270
but the Tao family

441
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,270
never has.

442
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,880
Thank you, Grandfather and Uncle.

443
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,270
I've grown up.

444
00:22:01,728 --> 00:22:03,550
The blood debt
owed by Prince Kang's Manor,

445
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,680
I should be the one to make them pay.

446
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,510
Xihe, you've only just arrived
in the imperial capital.

447
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,240
Countless eyes are on you.

448
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:12,510
You mustn't act rashly.

449
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:15,920
As long as my father and brother
remain in the northwest,

450
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,750
no matter how unhappy they are,

451
00:22:17,840 --> 00:22:18,880
they'll have to endure it.

452
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,240
Don't forget,

453
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:23,480
you still have
the Tao family behind you.

454
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:24,830
That's right.

455
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,160
Your Highness,

456
00:22:28,192 --> 00:22:29,510
Prince Yu requests an audience.

457
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,510
Xihe,

458
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,960
are you acquainted with Prince Yu?

459
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,880
I only met him once at today's banquet.

460
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:38,720
Then...

461
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:41,310
why would he come all the way here?

462
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:42,880
I don't know either.

463
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:46,160
Please invite Prince Yu inside.

464
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:47,070
Yes.

465
00:22:48,032 --> 00:22:49,880
- Greetings, Prince Yu.
- Greetings, Prince Yu.

466
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,640
You may all rise.

467
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:53,200
Your Highness as well.

468
00:22:54,576 --> 00:22:56,110
Your Highness has traveled a long way.

469
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:57,950
I'm afraid you may not
have brought everything you need.

470
00:22:57,968 --> 00:22:59,760
I'd like to offer
a small token of my regard.

471
00:22:59,770 --> 00:23:01,650
I didn't expect Master Tao
to be here as well.

472
00:23:01,664 --> 00:23:02,912
I hope Master Tao doesn't mind.

473
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,270
Of course not.

474
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:09,640
Prince Yu presents
Commandery Princess Zhaoning

475
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:12,510
with a glazed incense burner set
with milk-nail pattern.

476
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:14,656
(Imperial Apothecary)
One box of the finest incense.

477
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:18,880
This is an access token
to the Imperial Apothecary.

478
00:23:18,912 --> 00:23:20,980
From now on, whatever incense
Your Highness requires,

479
00:23:20,992 --> 00:23:22,480
just have your servants fetch it.

480
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,790
Thank you, Prince Yu.

481
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:32,830
Prince Yu also presents
Commandery Princess Zhaoning

482
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:34,640
with ten bolts of Mingxia Brocade.

483
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,590
This Mingxia Brocade

484
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:37,590
was offered as tribute
by the Nvman Kingdom.

485
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:40,000
Its radiant luster and rich fragrance
are truly exceptional.

486
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:42,830
I had it specially prepared
for Your Highness in advance.

487
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:45,880
Prince Yu also presents
Commandery Princess Zhaoning

488
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:47,830
with ten pomegranate lip rouges,

489
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:49,830
ten boxes of rose face powder,

490
00:23:49,830 --> 00:23:51,110
and a string of northern pearls

491
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:53,550
for Your Highness's toilette.

492
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:55,030
Prince Yu is so generous.

493
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:56,550
How could I ever repay you?

494
00:23:56,608 --> 00:23:57,960
Your Highness needn't be so polite.

495
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,200
These things

496
00:23:59,328 --> 00:24:00,880
are just a small token of my regard.

497
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:04,070
Thank you, Prince Yu.

498
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,750
It's getting late today.

499
00:24:08,110 --> 00:24:09,590
Perhaps we should meet another day.

500
00:24:14,112 --> 00:24:15,680
You are quite right, Your Highness.

501
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:18,336
Master Tao and Your Highness
have just reunited after so long.

502
00:24:19,168 --> 00:24:20,550
Then I won't disturb you.

503
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,952
I'll take my leave.

504
00:24:29,550 --> 00:24:31,160
I heard His Majesty

505
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:32,720
intends to choose a husband for you.

506
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:36,590
Prince Yu was so attentive today.

507
00:24:36,590 --> 00:24:37,440
Does he

508
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,030
intend to marry you?

509
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:41,216
I've only just arrived
in the imperial capital.

510
00:24:41,310 --> 00:24:43,880
I don't know much about the princes yet.

511
00:24:44,030 --> 00:24:45,000
I cannot decide.

512
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,160
The sons of the imperial family

513
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,400
are all far from simple.

514
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,270
Choosing a husband

515
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:52,640
must be done with great care.

516
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,700
(Prince Xin's Manor)

517
00:25:16,510 --> 00:25:17,160
Changqing,

518
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:20,110
your wife has been gone for three years.

519
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:22,030
Why do this to yourself?

520
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,310
What it feels like to love someone,

521
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:27,960
you didn't understand before.

522
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,720
But soon you will.

523
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,270
You want to get close

524
00:25:35,712 --> 00:25:37,552
to Commandery Princess Zhaoning,

525
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,830
yet you don't dare.

526
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,640
You want to show her kindness,

527
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,510
yet you don't know how.

528
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:45,750
The day she saved me,

529
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,350
I remembered her.

530
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:51,310
When she stole the Rouge Ledger,

531
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,590
I was angry,

532
00:25:53,110 --> 00:25:54,440
but I never truly blamed her.

533
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,680
When I went to see her today,

534
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,440
it confirmed what I had suspected.

535
00:25:59,450 --> 00:26:01,232
The commandery princess
took the Rouge Ledger

536
00:26:01,248 --> 00:26:03,296
to give it to someone
who would uphold justice.

537
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:04,480
Changqing,

538
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:06,070
you needn't pave the way for me.

539
00:26:06,912 --> 00:26:08,752
What the commandery princess is doing

540
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:10,720
is also what I wish to do.

541
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,920
You've truly fallen for her.

542
00:26:24,030 --> 00:26:25,070
I will help you.

543
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,790
I don't need your help.

544
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:28,880
The one you love is hard to come by.

545
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,510
Don't follow in my footsteps.

546
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:39,030
I don't want to see you
become who you are now.

547
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,880
My brother was once my greatest pride.

548
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,256
He was the man I admired most.

549
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:44,250
He was full of ambition,
always in complete command.

550
00:26:44,260 --> 00:26:46,390
Yet now, his eyes are filled
with the weariness of life.

551
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:48,260
He appears to have
found peace and contentment.

552
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,510
But in truth,

553
00:26:50,336 --> 00:26:52,032
he has simply grown tired of living.

554
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:56,960
I once wondered,

555
00:26:57,408 --> 00:26:59,790
(The Late Lady Gu)
why I could never warm Qingzhi's heart.

556
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:01,480
I felt wronged,

557
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,110
lost,

558
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:05,030
and tormented.

559
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:07,960
It wasn't until she passed away

560
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,270
that I finally understood.

561
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,240
Everything I gave

562
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:21,310
was nothing more than unrequited love.

563
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:25,200
What right did I have

564
00:27:28,944 --> 00:27:30,752
to expect her to return my feelings?

565
00:27:34,270 --> 00:27:35,030
Changqing,

566
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,480
let her go.

567
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,310
I can't.

568
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:54,720
Changying,

569
00:27:55,790 --> 00:27:57,270
I'm telling you this

570
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:01,110
because I hope you'll discover

571
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:04,440
what Commandery Princess Zhaoning
truly wants.

572
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:07,240
Don't let it slip away,

573
00:28:07,424 --> 00:28:08,880
and don't make the wrong choice.

574
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:12,310
I hope you'll find

575
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:17,750
the happiness I never had.

576
00:28:40,272 --> 00:28:40,920
Your Highness,

577
00:28:41,104 --> 00:28:42,608
the commandery princess has arrived.

578
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,310
You're here.

579
00:28:48,030 --> 00:28:49,200
I thought you weren't coming.

580
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,640
Your Highness.

581
00:28:53,408 --> 00:28:54,510
No need for formalities.

582
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:55,880
The wind is strong out here.

583
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:57,200
Let's talk inside.

584
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:57,720
Please.

585
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:11,790
The Crown Prince
truly has a gentle disposition.

586
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:14,030
He carries the grace
and refinement of a royal prince,

587
00:29:14,040 --> 00:29:16,870
yet none of the arrogance so often found
among those born to the throne.

588
00:29:18,600 --> 00:29:19,720
Your Highness, what's wrong?

589
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,160
I'm not afraid of bad people.

590
00:29:22,320 --> 00:29:24,240
I'm especially good
at fighting evil with evil.

591
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,480
But when it comes to good people,

592
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,160
I never quite know what to do.

593
00:29:30,704 --> 00:29:32,750
Commandery princess, this way, please.

594
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:45,312
Every flower and plant
in Your Highness's residence

595
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:46,720
is a rare and precious treasure.

596
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:49,070
You even diverted hot spring water here.

597
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:50,590
The flowers bloom in splendid beauty

598
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,990
through every season without fading.

599
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:56,350
You clearly know your flowers.

600
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:57,960
When did you develop
such refined tastes?

601
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,590
You're too kind, Your Highness.

602
00:30:00,200 --> 00:30:01,590
I've loved flowers and plants

603
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,750
ever since I was a child.

604
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,270
What a coincidence.

605
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,384
I've loved growing flowers and tending
plants since childhood as well.

606
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:10,470
From now on, you are always
welcome at the East Palace

607
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:11,712
to admire the beauty of flowers

608
00:30:11,728 --> 00:30:13,568
and appreciate the charm
of nature together.

609
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,880
(Commandery princess,)

610
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:18,640
(do you know
how this garden came to be?)

611
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:35,590
(I've put so much into it.)

612
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:17,350
Commandery princess, please.

613
00:31:27,110 --> 00:31:29,440
The tea glows with a bright apricot hue,

614
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:32,270
and its fragrance
is light and refreshing.

615
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:34,550
Preparing tea, burning incense,

616
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:36,330
arranging flowers,
and displaying paintings.

617
00:31:36,384 --> 00:31:38,110
Tea is what I do best.

618
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,590
Your Highness,

619
00:31:41,030 --> 00:31:41,750
this tea

620
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:44,350
is Wuyang tea personally grown
by Crown Prince.

621
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,720
Your Highness grows tea yourself?

622
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,310
When I was young,

623
00:31:51,790 --> 00:31:53,070
I fell gravely ill.

624
00:31:54,464 --> 00:31:57,184
I could neither excel in academics
nor martial arts like my brothers.

625
00:31:57,270 --> 00:31:58,480
My father pitied me,

626
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:00,350
so he entrusted state affairs to them

627
00:32:00,368 --> 00:32:02,064
and allowed me to focus on recovering.

628
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:04,270
Naturally, I came to appreciate

629
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,760
these seemingly useless pursuits.

630
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:06,590
Your Highness,

631
00:32:06,672 --> 00:32:08,160
the knowledge and skills one acquires

632
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,270
are meant to serve the realm.

633
00:32:09,590 --> 00:32:10,830
You need not belittle yourself.

634
00:32:11,872 --> 00:32:13,310
If Heaven has denied me something,

635
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:14,880
then I'll cherish what I have before me.

636
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:17,200
Enjoy today's happiness while it lasts.

637
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,750
I have something

638
00:32:25,936 --> 00:32:27,680
I'd like to present to Your Highness.

639
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:28,680
What is it?

640
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:44,740
(Rouge Ledger)

641
00:32:51,152 --> 00:32:53,200
This ledger records
the crimes of corrupt officials.

642
00:32:53,952 --> 00:32:55,240
Its contents are truly shocking.

643
00:32:56,480 --> 00:32:57,790
Where did you obtain it?

644
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,160
By a fortunate turn of fate.

645
00:33:00,030 --> 00:33:01,400
I'm entrusting it to Your Highness

646
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:03,110
because I believe

647
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,680
that once you have the Rouge Ledger,

648
00:33:04,736 --> 00:33:07,136
you will sweep away
corruption with decisive resolve.

649
00:33:07,152 --> 00:33:09,744
With a heart as impartial as a scale
and justice as steadfast as a mountain.

650
00:33:09,750 --> 00:33:12,500
However deeply rooted the corrupt
officials and greedy eunuchs may be,

651
00:33:12,510 --> 00:33:13,790
you will show them no mercy

652
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:15,120
and uproot them completely.

653
00:33:17,790 --> 00:33:19,240
We've only met twice,

654
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:20,110
yet you

655
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:22,200
trust me so completely?

656
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,550
For me,

657
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:24,880
one meeting is enough.

658
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:28,160
Besides, I trust my own judgment.

659
00:33:28,256 --> 00:33:30,510
And I trust in Your Highness's
integrity even more.

660
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:36,960
You are the first

661
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:38,720
to place hope in me,

662
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:40,310
a Crown Prince in name only.

663
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:42,350
I will do everything in my power

664
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:44,070
to live up to the faith

665
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,440
you have placed in me.

666
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:55,776
The commandery princess has returned
to the Duke of Wei's Manor.

667
00:33:56,992 --> 00:33:58,528
Your Highness expected this all along

668
00:33:58,830 --> 00:34:01,270
because you saw
that she trusted your character.

669
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,640
She was only putting on an act.

670
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,110
The real reason

671
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:10,760
is that she knows every other prince
has powerful forces behind

672
00:34:10,770 --> 00:34:12,620
and would inevitably
protect their own allies.

673
00:34:12,630 --> 00:34:14,360
Only someone like me,
who left the palace at a young age,

674
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:17,130
has no maternal family to rely on,
and stands apart from every faction,

675
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,280
can remain impartial,

676
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:19,280
without selfish motives,

677
00:34:19,344 --> 00:34:22,320
and bring every corrupt official
named in this ledger to justice.

678
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:23,440
Along the way,

679
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:25,984
I kept wondering how someone
could be so cold and rational.

680
00:34:26,110 --> 00:34:26,880
But today,

681
00:34:27,072 --> 00:34:29,456
I truly admire her unwavering
devotion to the greater good.

682
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:31,480
Your Highness,

683
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:34,670
Prince Yu followed the commandery
princess to the Duke of Wei's Manor

684
00:34:35,110 --> 00:34:36,510
with a cart full of gifts.

685
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:37,710
The commandery princess

686
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:38,832
accepted every single one.

687
00:34:39,312 --> 00:34:40,736
If he wants to give them, let him.

688
00:34:42,240 --> 00:34:43,710
Since Changyu offered them willingly,

689
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:46,030
accepting them is
simply showing him courtesy.

690
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,070
Exactly.

691
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:48,070
In short,

692
00:34:48,144 --> 00:34:50,096
whatever the commandery princess
does is right.

693
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:52,030
I know exactly what my brothers

694
00:34:52,030 --> 00:34:53,110
are thinking.

695
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:55,030
Whoever marries Shen Xihe

696
00:34:55,030 --> 00:34:56,760
will gain control
of the northwestern army.

697
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,890
Their intentions are far from honorable.

698
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:01,150
How could I let them have their way?

699
00:35:03,230 --> 00:35:04,590
As for Changyu,

700
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,710
it's time someone put him in his place.

701
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:10,780
(Sixian Hall)

702
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:15,690
After you, Changyu.

703
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:22,150
The tea carries a subtle fragrance.

704
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,440
I never expected

705
00:35:23,552 --> 00:35:25,552
Your Highness to be
so skilled in the art of tea.

706
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,920
Tea is said to cure all ailments.

707
00:35:28,230 --> 00:35:30,440
With my health,
I can hardly do without it.

708
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:32,832
The imperial capital is home
to many renowned physicians.

709
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,280
I'm sure the day will come

710
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:35,960
when Your Highness
makes a full recovery.

711
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:39,296
Thank you for your kind words, Changyu.

712
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,400
Speaking of the imperial capital,

713
00:35:48,816 --> 00:35:50,400
it truly is full of remarkable talents.

714
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:51,920
Today,

715
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:53,760
I met a musician

716
00:35:54,016 --> 00:35:55,936
who plays
the vertical konghou exquisitely.

717
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,550
I still remember that your mother

718
00:35:58,624 --> 00:36:00,416
was especially fond
of the vertical konghou.

719
00:36:00,496 --> 00:36:03,590
So I invited you here today
to enjoy the performance together.

720
00:36:05,264 --> 00:36:07,150
This musician's skill
on the vertical konghou,

721
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,800
though taught by you,

722
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:11,480
falls far short of yours.

723
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:23,280
Why does Your Highness say

724
00:36:23,710 --> 00:36:24,880
I taught this musician?

725
00:36:25,550 --> 00:36:27,190
What I have most is time.

726
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,800
When it comes to the vertical konghou,

727
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,000
I know a thing or two myself.

728
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,880
The techniques at your fingertips

729
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:32,710
are exactly the same.

730
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,480
This musician

731
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,920
is the qin instructor to

732
00:36:36,230 --> 00:36:37,590
Music Office dancer Bian Xianyi.

733
00:36:38,096 --> 00:36:40,480
Bian Xianyi's dancing is unrivaled
in the imperial capital.

734
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:42,096
She is only eighteen,

735
00:36:42,144 --> 00:36:44,550
yet no matter how many princes
and noble heirs seek her hand,

736
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:46,096
(Bian Xianyi, Dancer from Music Office)
she refuses them all.

737
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:49,230
Meanwhile, you have yet
to take a principal wife

738
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:52,590
and have twice declined Father's
arrangements for your marriage.

739
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:55,150
Could it be the two of you
made a promise to each other?

740
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:58,864
Why would Your Highness
make such baseless assumptions?

741
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,960
If you wanted to
take Bian Xianyi as a concubine,

742
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,360
it would be easy.

743
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,070
Yet you chose not to.

744
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,110
Could it be

745
00:37:06,208 --> 00:37:07,968
because you feared she would suffer?

746
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,670
As a prince,

747
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:12,550
you look beyond social rank.

748
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:15,550
I truly admire that about you, Changyu.

749
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:18,320
What exactly are you trying to imply?

750
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:20,510
I recently heard a story.

751
00:37:22,096 --> 00:37:24,360
A man first marries a noble lady
as his principal wife.

752
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:26,150
If she dies young,

753
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:28,280
or loses her life
in some tragic accident,

754
00:37:28,336 --> 00:37:30,784
he can then marry the woman
he truly loves as his second wife,

755
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,272
instead of making her a concubine.

756
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:33,440
What a fanciful tale.

757
00:37:34,656 --> 00:37:36,480
Even if my principal wife
were to pass away,

758
00:37:36,720 --> 00:37:37,960
a woman from the Music Office

759
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,872
could never become my second wife.

760
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:43,280
You must have already
thought that through.

761
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:44,960
If you married Shen Xihe

762
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:46,630
and secured the northwestern army,

763
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:48,480
with such a pillar
of the nation behind you,

764
00:37:48,528 --> 00:37:49,280
Father

765
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:51,550
might very well approve.

766
00:37:51,648 --> 00:37:54,070
That's nothing but groundless
speculation. None of it is true.

767
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:57,984
Besides, my feelings
for the commandery princess are sincere.

768
00:37:58,020 --> 00:37:59,140
She is the only one I love.

769
00:37:59,150 --> 00:38:00,960
Please don't question my sincerity.

770
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:01,952
I'll take my leave.

771
00:38:02,070 --> 00:38:03,320
Then why

772
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,550
are you wearing
Bian Xianyi's token of love?

773
00:38:05,584 --> 00:38:06,416
If I'm not mistaken,

774
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:08,840
the embroidered pattern
on that sachet is an entwining lotus,

775
00:38:08,840 --> 00:38:11,380
the very same design as the forehead
adornment Bian Xianyi wears.

776
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,920
You set me up?

777
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:25,590
So you've been gathering leverage
against me all along?

778
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,000
Changyu,

779
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:33,090
I've spent years away
from the palace recovering.

780
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:35,510
My brothers have never been close to me.

781
00:38:36,110 --> 00:38:37,360
The lonelier I felt,

782
00:38:37,660 --> 00:38:39,360
the more I cherished
the bond between us.

783
00:38:39,510 --> 00:38:41,100
I've always wanted what's best for you.

784
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:42,360
Is that truly how you see me?

785
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:45,480
It saddens me deeply.

786
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,280
Go on.

787
00:38:48,550 --> 00:38:49,480
Keep acting.

788
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,760
I may have wronged my wife,

789
00:38:51,856 --> 00:38:53,230
but I have never betrayed Xianyi.

790
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:55,230
Nor have I betrayed
the woman I truly love.

791
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:57,760
What's wrong with that?

792
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,840
I'm the one who's gravely ill.

793
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,880
Yet it seems
your condition is even worse.

794
00:39:04,030 --> 00:39:05,760
Such a thing, devoid of all humanity,

795
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:06,920
must never be done.

796
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,480
Then I simply

797
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,880
won't admit to any of it.

798
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,440
What can you possibly do to me?

799
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:25,550
You think there's nothing I can do?

800
00:39:29,792 --> 00:39:31,180
Tea is best enjoyed for its flavor.

801
00:39:31,190 --> 00:39:32,544
A play is best enjoyed
from beginning to end.

802
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:33,190
Your Highness.

803
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:34,760
Your Highness.

804
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,590
Your Highness!

805
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,360
Your Highness!

806
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:37,080
Your Highness!

807
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:38,920
Your Highness, what's wrong?

808
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:43,590
Your Highness!

809
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,230
Prince Yu, what have you done?

810
00:39:45,232 --> 00:39:47,424
You've angered him so badly
that he coughed up blood!

811
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,400
Someone!

812
00:39:48,590 --> 00:39:50,800
Prince Yu has made
the Crown Prince cough up blood!

813
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,070
- He's coughing up blood!
- Your Highness!

814
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,670
- Summon the Imperial Physician!
- Your Highness!

815
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:54,800
The Crown Prince has coughed up blood!

816
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:55,630
- Summon the Imperial Physician!
- Your Highness!

817
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:57,110
- Quick, summon the Imperial Physician!
- Your Highness, wake up!

818
00:39:57,110 --> 00:39:57,880
- Your Highness!
- Summon the Imperial Physician!

819
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,440
- Your Highness!
- His Highness has coughed up blood!

820
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,960
Your Highness!

821
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:17,424
Princes, if any of you admire
Commandery Princess Zhaoning,

822
00:40:17,488 --> 00:40:20,280
today is the perfect opportunity
to declare your feelings.

823
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:22,710
This Incense Record
is the finest of its kind.

824
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,880
I hope you will accept it.

825
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:26,110
If I should win your favor,

826
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:28,110
I swear to spend my life

827
00:40:28,128 --> 00:40:29,136
with only one wife.

828
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:30,000
And...

829
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:32,280
I, too, wish to ask
for your hand in marriage.

830
00:40:36,950 --> 00:40:39,890
♪I've hidden so many words♪

831
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:43,310
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

832
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:51,150
♪So never uncover♪

833
00:40:51,340 --> 00:40:53,700
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

834
00:40:54,830 --> 00:40:57,560
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

835
00:40:58,520 --> 00:41:03,860
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

836
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:08,440
♪Every answer I gave♪

837
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:12,090
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

838
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:16,250
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

839
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:19,820
♪How hard it truly was?♪

840
00:41:22,790 --> 00:41:26,230
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

841
00:41:27,220 --> 00:41:29,550
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

842
00:41:30,820 --> 00:41:36,580
♪Pretending to be brave
as if I'd never been hurt♪

843
00:41:37,990 --> 00:41:41,120
♪It's a shame I never could♪

844
00:41:41,570 --> 00:41:44,580
♪Give you a moon in return♪

845
00:41:44,690 --> 00:41:51,330
♪With the same open heart you loved me♪

846
00:41:51,330 --> 00:41:55,000
♪I've crossed the wasteland of memories♪

847
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:58,630
♪Never knowing I was lost♪

848
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:02,200
♪Why don't you take me away?♪

849
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:08,590
♪Lead me out of this endless game
of hide-and-seek♪

850
00:42:09,990 --> 00:42:13,540
♪You'll never♪

851
00:42:13,820 --> 00:42:23,290
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

